<fieldset class="fieldset">
  <Ui::Legend>
    <h2>&nbsp;Preparing the Racial Equity Report&nbsp;</h2>
  </Ui::Legend>

  Report guidance is available on <a href="https://www1.nyc.gov/site/planning/data-maps/edde/edde-overview.page">DCP's website</a>, the report must include:

  <br /><br />

  <ul>
    <li>A community profile downloaded from the <a href="https://equitableexplorer.planning.nyc.gov/map/data/district">Equitable Development Data Explorer (EDDE)</a></li>
    <li>A narrative statement of how the project relates to the City's goals and strategies to <a href="https://wherewelive.cityofnewyork.us/">affirmatively further fair housing</a></li>
    <li>Project specific data about anticipated housing units and jobs</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Please attach the Racial Equity Report as a PDF for your project
  </p>

  <Packages::ArtifactAttachments
    @artifact={{@model.project.artifact}}
    @fileManager={{@model.project.artifact.fileManager}}
    data-test-section="artifact-attachments"
  />
</fieldset>
